-- Bear Stearns see potential slowdown, not recession
-- 
-- Thu Oct 4, 2007 9:39am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/10/04/us-bearstearns-recession-idUSWEN147520071004

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Bear Stearns Cos BSC.N President Alan Schwartz said the odds are in favor of a potential slowdown in the economy, but not a recession. 

 Schwarz made the comments during the investment bank's investor day on Thursday. (Reporting by  Lilla Zuill )